@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
title Azure DevOps Wiki PlantUML Rendering Pipeline

actor Developer
participant "Azure Pipeline" as Pipeline
participant "Offline PlantUML" as Offline
participant "PlantUML Server" as Server
participant "Azure DevOps Wiki" as Wiki

Developer -> Pipeline: Commit diagram source
Pipeline -> Offline: Render -ttxt and inspect output
Offline --> Pipeline: ASCII representation
Pipeline -> Pipeline: grep -Ei "error|syntax"
Pipeline -> Server: GET /svg/{encoded}
Pipeline -> Server: GET /png/{encoded}
Server --> Pipeline: SVG + PNG
Pipeline -> Wiki: Publish artifacts
@enduml
